<i>[apprehensive music]</i>

33:51.905 --> 33:53.657
DESMOND:
Uh, fuck you.

33:53.657 --> 33:55.700
[cigarette sizzles]

33:58.495 --> 33:59.913
[dishes shatter]

33:59.913 --> 34:02.916
[indistinct arguing]

34:02.916 --> 34:09.631
<i>♪ ♪</i>

34:09.631 --> 34:11.299
What are you doing here,
Edwin?

34:11.299 --> 34:13.218
You have a problem.
SARA: So?

34:13.218 --> 34:15.136
EDWIN:
I can take care of it.

34:15.136 --> 34:16.763
SARA: You're only 14.

34:16.763 --> 34:18.431
You could not
possibly take care of this.

34:18.431 --> 34:22.102
Let's just say I have a way.

34:22.102 --> 34:25.563
Right, you a mobster
like your cousin?

34:25.563 --> 34:26.856
Maybe.

34:26.856 --> 34:28.483
You a fool.

34:28.483 --> 34:32.195
And why would you
do anything for me?

34:32.195 --> 34:34.072
I will want
something in return.

34:34.072 --> 34:35.448
I don't have any money.

34:35.448 --> 34:36.449
I know that.

34:38.827 --> 34:40.495
If I do this,

34:40.495 --> 34:42.914
you can never be with Gogo.

34:42.914 --> 34:44.291
Gogo?

34:44.291 --> 34:46.084
But why do you even care?

34:46.084 --> 34:53.091
<i>♪ ♪</i>

34:57.053 --> 34:59.681
EDWIN: It the queen
from the land West Chester.

35:03.768 --> 35:05.103
So you're talking to me now?

35:05.103 --> 35:08.148
<i>[soft suggestive music]</i>

35:08.148 --> 35:15.155
<i>♪ ♪</i>

35:29.919 --> 35:31.796
- Baby.
- What?

35:31.796 --> 35:33.715
I haven't had ten minutes
alone with you.

35:33.715 --> 35:35.258
I know.

35:35.258 --> 35:38.011
Somebody got to tell this
woman to stop invitin' herself

35:38.011 --> 35:39.804
on our vacations,

35:39.804 --> 35:42.140
and it needs to be you,
and you know why.

35:42.140 --> 35:44.642
- Why?
- Because you're white.

35:44.642 --> 35:47.354
[chuckles]
Touché. I will.

35:56.363 --> 35:58.323
Hi.
TYLER: Hey.

36:00.158 --> 36:01.409
Oh, thank you.

36:03.286 --> 36:07.540
You look
even hotter than usual.

36:07.540 --> 36:10.710
Thank you.
[chuckles]

36:10.710 --> 36:12.087
What?

36:13.088 --> 36:16.883
I'm just really
enjoying my vacation.

36:16.883 --> 36:17.967
[chuckles]

36:17.967 --> 36:20.970
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

36:20.970 --> 36:27.977
<i>♪ ♪</i>

37:07.767 --> 37:10.770
[indistinct chatter]
[camera shutters clicking]

37:10.770 --> 37:12.188
Wait.

37:12.188 --> 37:18.862
<i>♪ ♪</i>

37:20.321 --> 37:22.282
You sold your soul
for nothing.

37:22.282 --> 37:25.869
I'm going on <i>20/20.</i>
Your island is ruined anyway.

37:25.869 --> 37:27.078
[car door shuts]

37:27.078 --> 37:29.289
<i>EMILY:
When Alison went missing,</i>

37:29.289 --> 37:33.251
<i>I thought she was
playing a game or something.</i>

37:34.752 --> 37:37.547
<i>And then when
they brought her body back,</i>

37:37.547 --> 37:39.966
<i>it suddenly...</i>

37:39.966 --> 37:42.218
<i>became very real,</i>

37:42.218 --> 37:46.139
<i>and everything else
felt very unreal.</i>

37:49.100 --> 37:52.353
Like suddenly, everything
I believed was wrong.

37:55.315 --> 37:56.691
Like it was upside down.

38:00.945 --> 38:02.280
And I think I've--I...

38:04.491 --> 38:06.034
I've always felt like that.

38:06.034 --> 38:09.662
Yeah, but Emily,
when you act like

38:09.662 --> 38:14.292
somehow my loss
is less painful than yours--

38:14.292 --> 38:16.044
I mean, it feels so...

38:17.712 --> 38:18.713
Unfair.

38:20.590 --> 38:23.384
I know.

38:23.384 --> 38:24.511
And I'm sorry.

38:24.511 --> 38:27.514
<i>[soft pensive music]</i>

38:27.514 --> 38:29.557
<i>♪ ♪</i>

38:29.557 --> 38:33.269
So what does it mean
you're thinking about Alison?

38:33.269 --> 38:34.437
You're looking into it?

38:36.773 --> 38:39.359
The internet, the articles?

38:43.196 --> 38:44.656
Is there anything else?

38:46.115 --> 38:48.576
I will tell you.
I just can't right now.

38:48.576 --> 38:49.786
I just am not ready.

38:51.371 --> 38:52.747
[sighs]

38:54.916 --> 38:56.793
Can't say that doesn't hurt.

38:56.793 --> 38:59.754
I know. I'm sorry.

38:59.754 --> 39:03.132
Okay, I guess
I'll get back to work then.

39:03.132 --> 39:10.139
<i>♪ ♪</i>

39:17.480 --> 39:20.483
<i>[eerie music]</i>

39:20.483 --> 39:27.490
<i>♪ ♪</i>

39:38.334 --> 39:41.421
[scratching, chittering]

40:00.356 --> 40:02.275
<i>OMINOUS VOICE:
Gogo...</i>

40:05.194 --> 40:07.363
<i>[voice repeating "Gogo"]</i>

40:10.241 --> 40:12.201
<i>Gogo...</i>

40:14.370 --> 40:17.415
<i>Gogo...</i>

40:21.252 --> 40:24.756
[chittering]

40:31.471 --> 40:32.513
<i>Gogo!</i>

40:32.513 --> 40:36.017
[screaming]

40:36.017 --> 40:39.020
[panting]

40:40.521 --> 40:43.524
[breathing shakily]

40:43.524 --> 40:50.531
<i>♪ ♪</i>

41:02.877 --> 41:05.880
<i>[foreboding music]</i>

41:05.880 --> 41:12.887
<i>♪ ♪</i>

42:15.032 --> 42:16.034
<i>PERSON:
Woof!</i>

42:34.969 --> 42:37.096
<i>EMILY: My sister was murdered.</i>

42:37.096 --> 42:38.431
I just want answers.

42:38.431 --> 42:40.058
<i>You're a New York cab driver.</i>

42:40.058 --> 42:42.185
I mean, I'm sure you've got
a ton of crazy stories.

42:42.185 --> 42:43.311
A few.

42:43.311 --> 42:45.396
Play one game with me,
tell me a few.

42:45.396 --> 42:47.273
<i>SUNITA: And the thought of you
spending time</i>

42:47.273 --> 42:48.941
with that man, I just--

42:48.941 --> 42:51.527
Hey, it's gonna be fine.
I got this.

42:51.527 --> 42:52.945
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

42:52.945 --> 42:55.531
- I wanna see more of you.
- I'm working.

42:55.531 --> 42:57.950
<i>You go spend some time
with that college boy.</i>

42:57.950 --> 42:59.911
<i>ALISON: Just get the feeling
he's making fun of me.</i>

42:59.911 --> 43:02.330
<i>OLIVIA: Poor Alison--
one of her suitors isn't</i>

43:02.330 --> 43:03.915
worshipping the ground
that she walks on

43:03.915 --> 43:05.666
in a suitable fashion.

43:05.666 --> 43:07.251
Exactly.

43:07.251 --> 43:10.838
- Why my sister?
- Some things are inexplicable.

43:10.838 --> 43:13.341
<i>EMILY: I've been thinking
about how unfair it is</i>

43:13.341 --> 43:14.592
<i>we still don't have answers.</i>

43:14.592 --> 43:15.593
You know what, Em?

43:15.593 --> 43:17.345
I'm sorry
that your sister died,

43:17.345 --> 43:19.263
<i>but you're not eating,
you're not sleeping.</i>

43:19.263 --> 43:20.723
<i>EMILY: I'm outside
his apartment.</i>

43:20.723 --> 43:22.100
<i>I just need to figure out
how to get inside.</i>

43:22.100 --> 43:23.893
Oh, my God,
do you hear yourself?

43:23.893 --> 43:27.939
Your lucky day, big man.
I got a big surprise for you.

43:27.939 --> 43:29.106
No.

43:29.106 --> 43:30.650
All you need to do
is hold the drugs,

43:30.650 --> 43:32.360
and you will get
10% of my profits.

43:32.360 --> 43:33.736
I stopped going
to Dr. Norton.

43:33.736 --> 43:34.737
Wasn't she helping?

43:34.737 --> 43:36.155
I don't need to go to therapy

43:36.155 --> 43:37.782
to fix what's wrong with me.

43:37.782 --> 43:41.327
I need to fucking know
what happened to my sister.

43:41.327 --> 43:45.414
<i>♪ ♪</i>

43:45.414 --> 43:47.166
My life was ripped apart.

43:47.166 --> 43:48.584
Do you know what that's like?

43:48.584 --> 43:52.213
I know the feeling
of being...

43:52.213 --> 43:53.297
ripped apart.

43:53.297 --> 43:57.677
<i>♪ ♪</i>
